mentsh.

00:24:39.742 --> 00:24:41.272
zogt er "kum mit mir

00:24:41.784 --> 00:24:43.702
un du zog mir ver es tshepet dir."

00:24:44.163 --> 00:24:44.819
UNK

00:24:44.819 --> 00:24:47.460
farn hant. in di greys bin ikh bay im gevezn

00:24:47.488 --> 00:24:49.237
bizn

00:24:50.002 --> 00:24:50.686
halb.

00:24:50.666 --> 00:24:51.617
ye.

00:24:52.972 --> 00:24:54.316
zogt er "kum.

