00:25:10.893 --> 00:25:12.443
ikh, ikh'l aykh shoyn nit shisn.

00:25:12.443 --> 00:25:13.650
UNK mit eyn klap

00:25:13.650 --> 00:25:15.259
harge ikh oys alemen do."

00:25:17.070 --> 00:25:17.976
OKAY.

00:25:18.048 --> 00:25:20.028
rikhtik m'hot mir shoyn nit getshepet.

00:25:20.028 --> 00:25:22.717
moyre gehat az er vet gebn a patsh, a klap

00:25:22.790 --> 00:25:24.337
⟨der⟩ darfn zey nit shisn.

00:25:26.587 --> 00:25:30.530
ye, ikh bin avek; ah, ikh ze, dortn, ikh bin avek tsu a shnayder.

00:25:32.105 --> 00:25:34.175
ongeklapt, gey arayn.

00:25:35.058 --> 00:25:40.216
geven opgerisn bin ikh geven, ah, kh'hob oyfgeefnt di tir, hot men geheysn arayngeyn; ikh shtey lebn tir.

00:25:41.032 --> 00:25:43.878
kukn zey, un bay im nokh gearbet tsvey arbeter.

00:25:44.778 --> 00:25:48.265
zogt er tsu mir der balebos "vos shteystu do? kum

00:25:48.862 --> 00:25:50.156
kum gey vayter."

00:25:50.212 --> 00:25:52.906
⟨tsugegangen.⟩ zogt er "zets zikh." ⟨hot er⟩ gezetst.

00:25:52.980 --> 00:25:54.999
kukt er oyf mir; er hot shoyn farshtanen

00:25:56.321 --> 00:25:59.353
az, az do iz a tsore mit mir.

00:26:02.649 --> 00:26:05.473
zogt er bay mir

00:26:05.473 --> 00:26:07.419
fregt er "vi, vi UNK

00:26:07.627 --> 00:26:08.983
fun shtikl arbetn"

00:26:08.983 --> 00:26:11.098
fun shtikl, dos heyst yeder, yeder.

00:26:11.778 --> 00:26:13.325
"oder fun tog?"

00:26:13.854 --> 00:26:17.243
zog ikh "ikh vil nit arbetn fun tog; ikh vil nit arbetn fun shtikl

00:26:17.263 --> 00:26:18.290
farn esn."

00:26:18.290 --> 00:26:19.974
mir gebn a shtikl broyt vet zayn gut.

00:26:20.672 --> 00:26:24.463
hot er oyf mir a kuk geton, ale kukn oyf, di arbeter zogn

00:26:24.755 --> 00:26:26.791
er iz a meshugener vayzt oys.

00:26:27.911 --> 00:26:30.572
nor er zet az ikh bin nit keyn meshugener.

00:26:30.982 --> 00:26:33.373
fregt er bay mir "fun vanen bistu?"

00:26:33.615 --> 00:26:36.022
az d- az ikh reyd azoy.

00:26:36.315 --> 00:26:40.629
hob ikh im sh- im hob ikh gezogt az ikh bin antlofn fun grub; ikh darf nit hobn keyn gelt.

00:26:41.529 --> 00:26:42.631
ikh bin a hungeriker.

00:26:42.631 --> 00:26:43.582
UNK

00:26:44.398 --> 00:26:46.260
hot er a geshrey geton di vayb

00:26:46.305 --> 00:26:47.542
"gey arayn in kikh.

00:26:47.553 --> 00:26:49.289
gib dem yat

00:26:49.289 --> 00:26:50.028
esn."

00:26:50.574 --> 00:26:52.841
gedenk ikh nit un UNK dokh a mol alts

00:26:52.841 --> 00:26:54.315
borsht ⟨flegn zey makhn⟩.

00:26:55.248 --> 00:26:57.065
un UNK gehat.

00:26:59.585 --> 00:27:00.865
ikh hob zikh ongegesn.

00:27:00.865 --> 00:27:01.777
oy, ikh hob zikh

00:27:01.777 --> 00:27:03.900
gekumen tsu zikh a bisl opgekhapt di harts.

00:27:04.935 --> 00:27:09.935
"ye, git mir oykh a, nem a por PAIRS." ikh hob genumen di PAIRS, di hoyzn

00:27:09.963 --> 00:27:11.117
in di hent; hot er

00:27:11.145 --> 00:27:13.620
ge- shoyn gezen az ikh gey shoyn nemen.

00:27:13.676 --> 00:27:14.362
ye.

00:27:14.756 --> 00:27:17.805
vayle dan hob ikh UNK zikh oysgelernt hoyzn.

00:27:20.493 --> 00:27:24.844
nor vos z- zog ikh im az ikh vil makhn a por

00:27:24.844 --> 00:27:25.787
shtivl.

00:27:27.176 --> 00:27:28.503
proste shtivl.

00:27:28.982 --> 00:27:32.081
⟨az ikh⟩ zol kenen arumdreyen shmates

00:27:34.263 --> 00:27:39.202
zog ikh vayle ikh vil fun danet antloyfn, oyb ikh vel kenen antloyfn in di velder.

00:27:40.187 --> 00:27:41.003
rikhtik.

00:27:41.003 --> 00:27:44.940
hot er mir gegebn ⟨ah, epes⟩ gelt hot er mir gegebn rikhtik ikh zol geyn

00:27:45.030 --> 00:27:46.729
⟨epes⟩ makhn a por shtivl.

00:27:46.920 --> 00:27:47.792
UNK arayn

00:27:48.202 --> 00:27:49.850
es zitst dort der shuster un

00:27:50.430 --> 00:27:51.639
makht shtivl.

00:27:52.083 --> 00:27:53.346
"ye, gut morgn."

00:27:53.366 --> 00:27:54.137
"gut morgn."

